General.Name: J.R.W. Utility Public Company Limited
General.Description: J.R.W. Utility Public Company Limited engages in the design, procurement, construction, and installation of electrical power and telecommunication, and information technology systems. It operates through two segments, Sales of Electronics Equipment and Contract Services. The company is involved in high voltage transmission line system construction; high voltage substation construction and equipment installation; construction for changing the power lines to the underground systems; and infrastructure system planning, core network system, software and application system construction, and Systematization of other devices. It also maintains, repairs, and sells electrical system equipment, and telecommunication and information technology systems. In addition, the company engages in the contractor, consultation, inspection, and trading and distribution of tools, equipment, and materials related to civil, mechanical, electronic, and security equipment. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.
